00:03:09.000 --> 00:03:14.000
Emanuele Crialese won the Special Jury Prize for Terraferma,

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:16.000
the film talks about the landings in Lampedusa,

00:03:16.000 --> 00:03:19.000
seen through the eyes of Sicilian fishermen.

00:03:19.000 --> 00:03:21.000
The director said he was honored and delighted and

00:03:21.000 --> 00:03:26.000
thanked the interpreters of the film, Giuseppe Fiorello and Donatella Finocchiaro.

